<br>
After that I would take one healer (usually a cleric or druid) and just start to make groups from there.<br>
<br>
One thing you used to have to worry about was forming a KS group, or making one group all wizards or rogues or what have you because they would end up taking 90% of the exp for kills and sometimes it would cause animosity on the person who made the groups by jealous groups that got no exp(especially if you made it into said group).  Because of that I always tried to balance the damage around.<br>
